# Cloudflare Pages redirects for boxd-card.com
#
# The apex (docs/index.html) IS the marketing landing page — served directly as
# a static asset. (Cloudflare Pages does not honor a `/ -> /landing/index.html`
# 200 rewrite, so the landing lives at the apex rather than behind a rewrite.)

# The interim /landing/ path and the retired /about page fold into the apex.
# Exact matches only — do not use a splat here, or /landing/assets/* would break.
/landing       /          301
/landing/      /          301
/about         /          301
/about/        /          301

# Legacy flat privacy path → new directory location.
/privacy.html  /privacy   301
